  <h2 class="text-center text-lg font-bold my-2">What is Turkish for Indie Game Developers?</h2>

  <p>
    In short, TIGD is a English-Turkish online dictionary for small-scale games and developers. We aim to improve the
    translation quality of machine-translated games by providing free categorised translation memories, an online
    dictionary and a community for post-translation editing. You can translate your small-scale games that do not
    need dialogue translation accurately through the tools we offer you, and then you can send us your suggestions
    and requests from the community we have created on the reddit platform and our website. We will continue to
    expand our online dictionary in line with your requests and suggestions.
  </p>
  <br>
