  <h2 class="text-center font-bold my-2 text-lg"> How To Use</h2>

  <p>
    You can use the translation memories that we have shared on Reddit or here on the website to translate your
    games by running them through any computer assisted translation software in accordance with their categories,
    and then you can correct the errors caused by conflicts by looking at the explanations from the dictionary. After
    following these steps, you can share with us the texts you would like us to examine and correct on the Reddit
    platform.
